{"id":2981,"date":"2025-06-05T13:37:02","date_gmt":"2025-06-05T06:37:02","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=2981"},"modified":"2025-06-09T10:19:11","modified_gmt":"2025-06-09T03:19:11","slug":"mun-boc-la-gi","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/thong-tin-nganh\/mun-boc-la-gi\/","title":{"rendered":"M\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc l\u00e0 g\u00ec? V\u00ec sao kh\u00f3 tr\u1ecb v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch x\u1eed l\u00fd hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ec3 n\u1eb7ng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u1ee5n tr\u1ee9ng c\u00e1 c\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u, s\u01b0ng vi\u00eam v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i s\u1eb9o. Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eed \u0111\u1ee7 c\u00e1ch nh\u01b0ng m\u1ee5n v\u1eabn t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t, k\u00e9o d\u00e0i su\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m, khi\u1ebfn l\u00e0n da ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111ang loay hoay trong v\u00f2ng lu\u1ea9n qu\u1ea9n c\u1ee7a m\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc, \u0111\u1eebng v\u1ed9i n\u1ea3n l\u00f2ng. B\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 m\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc l\u00e0 g\u00ec v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc s\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ecf hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.\u00a0<\/span><\/i><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"mun-boc-la-gi\"><\/span><b>M\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t d\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng, c\u00f3 k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1edbn (th\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1eeb 0.5 cm tr\u1edf l\u00ean), b\u00ean trong ch\u1ee9a m\u1ee7 ho\u1eb7c m\u00e1u. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i m\u1ee5n h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh khi vi khu\u1ea9n Cutibacterium acnes (C. acnes) x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp v\u00e0o nang l\u00f4ng b\u1ecb t\u1eafc ngh\u1ebdn, g\u00e2y vi\u00eam nhi\u1ec5m s\u00e2u d\u01b0\u1edbi da. M\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc th\u01b0\u1eddng xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u1edf c\u00e1c v\u00f9ng da c\u00f3 tuy\u1ebfn b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0 m\u1eb7t, c\u1ed5, l\u01b0ng v\u00e0 ng\u1ef1c.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3779\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3779\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3779\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/20-1.webp\" alt=\"M\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc l\u00e0 g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/20-1.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/20-1-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/20-1-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/20-1-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3779\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">M\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc l\u00e0 g\u00ec<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch, m\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c bi\u1ebfn ch\u1ee9ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 \u00e1p xe, t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f4 s\u00e2u, \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i th\u00e2m s\u1eb9o l\u00e2u d\u00e0i v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dau-hieu-nhan-biet-mun-boc-tu-chuyen-gia\"><\/span><b>D\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u nh\u1eadn bi\u1ebft m\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc t\u1eeb chuy\u00ean gia<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n m\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u1ed1t m\u1ee5n s\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ecf, c\u00f3 k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1edbn: Khi s\u1edd v\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ed1i u c\u1ee9ng d\u01b0\u1edbi da.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110au nh\u1ee9c, c\u0103ng t\u1ee9c v\u00f9ng da quanh m\u1ee5n: M\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc th\u01b0\u1eddng r\u1ea5t \u0111au, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi ch\u1ea1m v\u00e0o.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u1ee9a m\u1ee7 ho\u1eb7c m\u00e1u b\u00ean trong: M\u1ee5n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 d\u1ecbch m\u00e0u v\u00e0ng, tr\u1eafng ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u00f4i khi l\u1eabn m\u00e1u.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u1ec5 v\u1ee1 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i s\u1eb9o th\u00e2m: M\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 vi\u00eam nhi\u1ec5m n\u1eb7ng n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch, d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1eb9o l\u1ed3i, s\u1eb9o l\u00f5m.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"2-nhom-mun-boc-pho-bien-hien-nay\"><\/span><b>2 nh\u00f3m m\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7n nay<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Nhi\u1ec1u n\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft m\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc l\u00e0 g\u00ec, m\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc c\u00f3 t\u1ef1 x\u1eb9p kh\u00f4ng hay m\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc c\u00f3 m\u1ea5y d\u1ea1ng? M\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t d\u1ea1ng duy nh\u1ea5t, m\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chia th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u lo\u1ea1i kh\u00e1c nhau t\u00f9y theo \u0111\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 vi\u00eam nhi\u1ec5m:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3780\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3780\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3780\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/20-2-3.webp\" alt=\"2 nh\u00f3m m\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7n nay\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/20-2-3.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/20-2-3-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/20-2-3-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/20-2-3-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3780\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">2 nh\u00f3m m\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7n nay<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"mun-boc-co-nhan\"><\/span><b><i>M\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc c\u00f3 nh\u00e2n<\/i><\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m: N\u1ed1t m\u1ee5n c\u1ee9ng, s\u1ea7n, s\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ecf nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1ee5n l\u1ed9 ra tr\u00ean b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Nh\u00e2n m\u1ee5n n\u1eb1m s\u00e2u trong da, g\u00e2y \u0111au nh\u1ee9c khi ch\u1ea1m v\u00e0o.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc m\u1ee7 &#8211; L\u00fac \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00e0 n\u1ed1t s\u1ea7n c\u1ee9ng, sau \u0111\u00f3 m\u1ec1m m\u1ecdng do ch\u1ee9a m\u1ee7 tr\u1eafng ho\u1eb7c xanh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u01b0\u1eddng do vi khu\u1ea9n ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, g\u00e2y vi\u00eam nhi\u1ec5m n\u1eb7ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"mun-boc-khong-nhan\"><\/span><b><i>M\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc kh\u00f4ng nh\u00e2n<\/i><\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc c\u00f3 m\u00e1u &#8211; Khi m\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc vi\u00eam s\u00e2u, c\u00e1c m\u1ea1ch m\u00e1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a b\u1ea1ch c\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ed1ng vi\u00eam, d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a m\u00e1u trong nh\u00e2n m\u1ee5n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ee5n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u1eeba ch\u1ee9a m\u1ee7, v\u1eeba c\u00f3 m\u00e1u, g\u00e2y c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c \u0111au nh\u1ee9c d\u1eef d\u1ed9i.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc chai l\u00ec (m\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc b\u1ecb chai) &#8211; M\u1ee5n s\u01b0ng to nh\u01b0ng c\u1ee9ng, dai d\u1eb3ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng x\u1eb9p.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">H\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh do l\u1edbp s\u1eebng tr\u00ean b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da t\u0103ng sinh qu\u00e1 m\u1ee9c ho\u1eb7c do th\u00f3i quen n\u1eb7n m\u1ee5n sai c\u00e1ch. Da v\u00f9ng n\u00e0y tr\u1edf n\u00ean th\u00f4 r\u00e1p, kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u, g\u00e2y m\u1ea5t th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"nguyen-nhan-hinh-thanh-mun-boc\"><\/span><b>Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc l\u00e0 g\u00ec v\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh ra sao? M\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc kh\u00f4ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n m\u00e0 l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng, c\u1ea3 b\u00ean trong l\u1eabn b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i c\u01a1 th\u1ec3. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn nh\u1ea5t khi\u1ebfn m\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng:<\/span><\/p>\n<ol>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R\u1ed1i lo\u1ea1n ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng b\u00e0i ti\u1ebft: Khi gan v\u00e0 th\u1eadn, hai c\u01a1 quan th\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9c ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng k\u00e9m, \u0111\u1ed9c t\u1ed1 t\u00edch t\u1ee5 s\u1ebd \u201cbi\u1ec3u t\u00ecnh\u201d qua da. L\u00e0n da s\u1ea3n sinh nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba h\u01a1n b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng, k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n, t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch s\u1ebd b\u00edt t\u1eafc l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng, t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho vi khu\u1ea9n ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n v\u00e0 h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0103n u\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 sinh ho\u1ea1t thi\u1ebfu khoa h\u1ecdc: Th\u1ee9c khuya, ng\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 gi\u1ea5c, \u0103n nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed3 chi\u00ean r\u00e1n, cay n\u00f3ng hay \u0111\u1ed3 \u0103n nhanh \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0m r\u1ed1i lo\u1ea1n n\u1ed9i ti\u1ebft t\u1ed1. Stress k\u00e9o d\u00e0i c\u0169ng l\u00e0m t\u0103ng n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 cortisol, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 m\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc \u1edf m\u1eb7t, l\u01b0ng v\u00e0 v\u00f9ng quai h\u00e0m.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Vi khu\u1ea9n Cutibacterium acnes (C. acnes): Khi vi khu\u1ea9n C. acnes x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp, c\u01a1 ch\u1ebf t\u1ef1 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a da s\u1ebd k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng vi\u00eam \u0111\u1ec3 \u201cch\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i k\u1ebb th\u00f9\u201d, d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc m\u1ee7, s\u01b0ng \u0111au.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3781\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3781\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3781\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/20-3-3.webp\" alt=\"Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc\" width=\"800\" height=\"581\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/20-3-3.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/20-3-3-300x218.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/20-3-3-768x558.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/20-3-3-600x436.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3781\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ol>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 di truy\u1ec1n: N\u1ebfu cha m\u1eb9 t\u1eebng c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n s\u1eed m\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc k\u00e9o d\u00e0i v\u00e0 dai d\u1eb3ng, b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 cao b\u1ecb m\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc do di truy\u1ec1n. D\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5n n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f3 x\u1eed l\u00fd d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m, d\u1ec5 t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ph\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u1ea7u th\u1eeba v\u00e0 b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn ti\u1ebft qu\u00e1 m\u1ee9c: Khi tuy\u1ebfn b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n d\u1eady th\u00ec, khi mang thai ho\u1eb7c trong k\u1ef3 kinh nguy\u1ec7t da s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 n\u1ed5i m\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc. Khu v\u1ef1c m\u00e1, tr\u00e1n v\u00e0 c\u1eb1m th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 \u201c\u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00f3ng\u201d do b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn t\u1eadp trung nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n v\u00e0 c\u1eb7n trang \u0111i\u1ec3m: L\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch da kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch khi\u1ebfn b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n, m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m d\u01b0 th\u1eeba t\u00edch t\u1ee5 s\u00e2u trong l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng. L\u00e2u ng\u00e0y, l\u1edbp bi\u1ec3u b\u00ec b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, vi khu\u1ea9n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i sinh s\u00f4i, d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc vi\u00eam.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1ef1 m\u1ea5t c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng n\u1ed9i ti\u1ebft t\u1ed1: Hormone androgen t\u0103ng cao trong c\u00e1c giai \u0111o\u1ea1n nh\u01b0 d\u1eady th\u00ec, mang thai ho\u1eb7c do c\u00e1c b\u1ec7nh l\u00fd (h\u1ed9i ch\u1ee9ng bu\u1ed3ng tr\u1ee9ng \u0111a nang, r\u1ed1i lo\u1ea1n n\u1ed9i ti\u1ebft) c\u0169ng l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n k\u00edch th\u00edch tuy\u1ebfn b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1ea1nh, khi\u1ebfn m\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cach-tri-mun-boc-sung-do-hieu-qua-tu-chuyen-gia\"><\/span><b>C\u00e1ch tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc s\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ecf hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1eeb chuy\u00ean gia<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc l\u00e0 g\u00ec &#8211; Ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da khoa h\u1ecdc v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1eeba m\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc t\u1eeb s\u1edbm s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng vi\u00eam nhi\u1ec5m v\u00e0 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u00e1c bi\u1ebfn ch\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i s\u1eb9o. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p ch\u0103m s\u00f3c v\u00e0 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng ngay:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3782\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3782\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3782\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/20-4-3.webp\" alt=\"C\u00e1ch tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc s\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ecf hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1eeb chuy\u00ean gia\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/20-4-3.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/20-4-3-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/20-4-3-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/20-4-3-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3782\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">M\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc s\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ecf hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1eeb chuy\u00ean gia<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"rua-mat-nhe-nhang-dung-cach\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R\u1eeda m\u1eb7t nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng, \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u1ec9 r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t t\u1ed1i \u0111a 2 l\u1ea7n m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 t\u1ed1i b\u1eb1ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9a c\u1ed3n hay h\u01b0\u01a1ng li\u1ec7u g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng. Th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c thao t\u00e1c nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng, tr\u00e1nh ch\u00e0 x\u00e1t m\u1ea1nh l\u00ean v\u00f9ng da c\u00f3 m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf vi\u00eam nhi\u1ec5m n\u1eb7ng h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tay-trang-ky-luong-moi-ngay\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u1ea9y trang k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Lu\u00f4n t\u1ea9y trang tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111i ng\u1ee7, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t sau khi trang \u0111i\u1ec3m ho\u1eb7c ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u00f4 nhi\u1ec5m. D\u00f9ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m t\u1ea9y trang ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi lo\u1ea1i da n\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ea9y trang cho da d\u1ea7u m\u1ee5n, d\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang cho da kh\u00f4\u00a0 \u0111\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn, b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n v\u00e0 c\u1eb7n trang \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u00edch t\u1ee5 trong l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"bao-ve-da-bang-kem-chong-nang\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da b\u1eb1ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng h\u1eb1ng ng\u00e0y, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi tr\u1eddi r\u00e2m m\u00e1t. Ch\u1ecdn kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng c\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 SPF t\u1eeb 30 tr\u1edf l\u00ean, ph\u1ed5 r\u1ed9ng (b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da kh\u1ecfi c\u1ea3 tia UVA v\u00e0 UVB) v\u00e0 k\u1ebft c\u1ea5u m\u1ecfng nh\u1eb9 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi l\u00e0n da m\u1ee5n.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3783\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3783\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3783\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/20-5-3.webp\" alt=\"B\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da b\u1eb1ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/20-5-3.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/20-5-3-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/20-5-3-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/20-5-3-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3783\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">B\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da b\u1eb1ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"trang-diem-an-toan-han-che-gay-bit-tac-da\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Trang \u0111i\u1ec3m an to\u00e0n, h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf g\u00e2y b\u00edt t\u1eafc da<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u00f9ng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m trang \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9a d\u1ea7u (oil-free), c\u00f3 k\u1ebft c\u1ea5u m\u1ecfng nh\u1eb9.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tr\u00e1nh c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 h\u01b0\u01a1ng li\u1ec7u m\u1ea1nh ho\u1eb7c c\u1ed3n kh\u00f4, v\u00ec d\u1ec5 khi\u1ebfn da k\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u00e0 m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam tr\u1edf n\u00ean n\u1eb7ng h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"khong-tu-y-nan-mun\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00f4ng t\u1ef1 \u00fd n\u1eb7n m\u1ee5n<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ef1 \u00fd n\u1eb7n m\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 khi m\u1ee5n ch\u01b0a ch\u00edn ho\u1eb7c \u0111ang s\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ecf. Khi n\u1ed1t m\u1ee5n c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kem ch\u1ea5m m\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 kh\u00f4 c\u1ed3i m\u1ee5n nh\u00e9.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3784\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3784\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3784\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/20-6.webp\" alt=\"Kh\u00f4ng t\u1ef1 \u00fd n\u1eb7n m\u1ee5n\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/20-6.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/20-6-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/20-6-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/20-6-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3784\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Kh\u00f4ng t\u1ef1 \u00fd n\u1eb7n m\u1ee5n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf m\u1ee5n an to\u00e0n, h\u00e3y \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c c\u01a1 s\u1edf da li\u1ec5u uy t\u00edn \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u00fang k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i s\u1eb9o.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"lua-chon-san-pham-duong-da-phu-hop\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m d\u01b0\u1ee1ng da ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t: \u01afu ti\u00ean c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i ch\u1ee9a ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t kh\u00e1ng vi\u00eam (nh\u01b0 Salicylic Acid, Tea Tree Oil), gi\u00fap l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m m\u1ea5t \u0111i \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean c\u1ee7a da.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3769\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3769\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3769\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/23-5-2.webp\" alt=\"Duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m cho l\u00e0n da\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/23-5-2.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/23-5-2-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/23-5-2-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/23-5-2-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3769\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m cho l\u00e0n da<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Toner: Ch\u1ecdn toner c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n t\u1eeb c\u00e2y ph\u1ec9 (Witch Hazel), gi\u00fap se kh\u00edt l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng, kh\u00e1ng khu\u1ea9n v\u00e0 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng pH.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m: S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng d\u1ea1ng gel ho\u1eb7c lotion \u0111\u1ec3 cung c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y b\u00edt t\u1eafc l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft: \u01afu ti\u00ean s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ee9a AHA\/BHA \u0111\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng, h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf s\u1eebng h\u00f3a v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m nguy c\u01a1 h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"giu-gin-ve-sinh-ca-nhan-va-khong-gian-song\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Gi\u1eef g\u00ecn v\u1ec7 sinh c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean gi\u1eb7t ch\u0103n, g\u1ed1i, kh\u0103n m\u1eb7t\u00a0 nh\u1eefng v\u1eadt d\u1ee5ng ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi da \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba vi khu\u1ea9n sinh s\u00f4i.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tr\u00e1nh ch\u1ea1m tay l\u00ean m\u1eb7t li\u00ean t\u1ee5c, v\u00ec b\u00e0n tay l\u00e0 n\u01a1i ch\u1ee9a nhi\u1ec1u vi khu\u1ea9n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc tr\u1edf n\u00ean nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ket-luan\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">To\u00e0n b\u1ed9 ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn <\/span><b>m\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc \u1edf m\u1eb7t <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c GSC chia s\u1ebb t\u1edbi c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. Ngo\u00e0i ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1<\/span><b> m\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc l\u00e0 g\u00ec <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da chia s\u1ebb t\u1edbi n\u00e0ng, c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00f3n ch\u1edd nh\u00e9!<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111ang loay hoay trong v\u00f2ng lu\u1ea9n qu\u1ea9n c\u1ee7a m\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc, \u0111\u1eebng v\u1ed9i n\u1ea3n l\u00f2ng. B\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 m\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc l\u00e0 g\u00ec v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc s\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ecf hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.\u00a0<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":7,"featured_media":3778,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[16],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-2981","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-thong-tin-nganh"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2981","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/7"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2981"}],"version-history":[{"count":4,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2981\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":3976,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2981\/revisions\/3976"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3778"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2981"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=2981"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=2981"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}